<script>
    (function(){
        // footer处理

        var locale = window.__locale;
        if(locale === 'ar_MA')locale = 'ar_SA';
        if(locale === 'iw_IL')locale = 'he_IL';
    
        // 页面滚动
        var pageContainer = document.querySelector('#content');
        function setFooter(){
            var footer = document.querySelector('[data-locale="' + locale + '"][data-temp-footer]');
            var urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
            var isHideHeader = urlParams.get("hideHeader");
            if (!footer || isHideHeader === 'true') return;
            footer.style.display = 'block';
            footer.removeAttribute('data-temp-footer');
            var otherFooter = document.querySelectorAll('[data-temp-footer]');
            for(var i = 0; i < otherFooter.length;i++) {
                otherFooter[i].parentNode.removeChild(otherFooter[i]);
            }
        }
        setFooter()
        if (pageContainer) {
            var pageContainerHeight = 0;
            var needResend = false;
            document.addEventListener('scroll', function(e) {
                var rect = pageContainer.getBoundingClientRect();
                var innerHeight = window.innerHeight;
                if (pageContainerHeight !== rect.height) {
                    // 容器高度发生了变化
                    pageContainerHeight = rect.height;
                    needResend = true;
                }
                window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('onListScroll', {detail: e}));
                if (needResend && rect.bottom < innerHeight + 500) {
                    needResend = false;
                    window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('onListEndReached', {detail: e}));
                }
            });
        }
        window.scriptLoadTimeStart = Date.now()
    }());
</script>
